Package com.atakmap.android.util

Class TimeTrackingProcessService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.util.TimeTrackingProcessService
  • public class TimeTrackingProcessService
extends java.lang.Object
    Service for gating less "up-to-date" times from triggering some processing done by the calling user code. The current and most common use is the CotImporterManager can throw out events that should not apply since they are out of date.

        public TimeTrackingProcessService.PendingToken begin​(@NonNull
                                                     java.lang.String uid,
                                                     @NonNull
                                                     CoordinatedTime time)
        Begin a process with a given time. The result of begin is 'null' when a process exists that already has a greater time OR a time record exists with a later time.
        Parameters:
        uid - Unique CoT Event ID
        time - CoT time to consider as latest pending process
        Returns:
        an instance of PendingToken IFF the time supersedes the current time record or no process is pending and no time record exists.

                                                     java.lang.String uid,

        Begin a process with a given time. The result of begin is 'null' when a process exists that already has a greater time OR a time record exists with a later time.
        Parameters:
        uid - Unique CoT Event ID
        timestamp - CoT time to consider as latest pending process

        Returns:
        an instance of PendingToken IFF the time supersedes the current time record or no process is pending and no time record exists.

      • commit

        public boolean commit​(@NonNull
                      TimeTrackingProcessService.PendingToken token)
        Commit a pending process
        Parameters:
        token - the pending process token
        Returns:
        true if committed as the latest time record, otherwise false if it was rejected as there is a later token pending
